[This has been a very bad year with regard to the virulence of the
Hendra virus. It would seem that declaring the virus endemic in 2
states would be a way of putting people on permanent alert. In other
words, they should always have that disease as one of the
differentials regarding horse illnesses.

Hopefully the vaccine will be available soon. Also hopefully some of
these projects will pay dividends and provide answers to the many
questions about Hendra virus. - Mod.TG]
